Bring a nostalgic charm to your browser with the Sunset Pixel Live Wallpaper. This stunning wallpaper captures the serene glow of a pixelated sunset, blending retro artistry with peaceful vibes. Perfect for lovers of pixel art and breathtaking evening horizons, this extension adds a soothing ambiance to your browsing experience.

Key Features
🌄 Pixel-Art Sunset: A mesmerizing retro-style sunset to relax your eyes and inspire your mind.
🔍 Google Search Bar: Smoothly integrated into the sunset design for effortless browsing.
🕒 Clock & Date: Minimalist time display to keep you organized without disrupting the aesthetic.
🌐 Customizable Shortcuts: Tailor your new tab with shortcuts that suit your needs.
🔗 Manage Extensions: Convenient links for "Remove Extension" and "More Extensions" at the bottom-left corner.
Let the calming hues of the Sunset Pixel Live Wallpaper transform your everyday browsing into a moment of retro relaxation. It’s a perfect choice for pixel art fans and those who appreciate the beauty of twilight.
